sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Aplicação terceira
    participant API as Lightcode Registration API
    participant Tenant as TenantLookup
    participant Cred as UserCredentialValidator
    participant Policy as AuthSchemaTwoFactorPolicy
    participant MFA as TwoFactorSettingsService
    participant JWT as AccessTokenIssuer
    participant RT as RefreshTokenRepository

    App->>API: POST /api/auth/token grant_type=password
    API->>Tenant: Validar X-Tenant-Id e tenant ativo
    Tenant-->>API: Tenant válido
    API->>Cred: Validar username, password, status e e-mail confirmado
    Cred-->>API: Usuário válido
    API->>Policy: Resolver auth.twoFactor.mode pelo schema do usuário
    Policy-->>API: mode=disabled ou mode=optional
    API->>MFA: Consultar configuração individual do usuário
    MFA-->>API: 2FA individual desativado
    API->>JWT: Emitir access token com amr=pwd
    API->>RT: Criar refresh token para subjectType=user
    API-->>App: access_token, refresh_token, token_type, expires_in

    Note over API: Sem 2FA obrigatório no schema e sem ativação individual, o login segue sem challenge.
